WEBVTT

00:10.534 --> 00:11.632
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF"...</i>

00:11.634 --> 00:13.132
I'M GONNA ASK YOUR MOTHER
TO MARRY ME.

00:13.134 --> 00:14.898
YES.

00:14.900 --> 00:17.432
YOU REMEMBER WHAT I TOLD YOU,
WHAT I WAS GONNA TELL DANTE?

00:17.434 --> 00:19.165
EITHER HE MAKES A STATEMENT,
OR I LEAVE.

00:19.167 --> 00:21.632
HE TOLD ME TO GET OUT.
MAKE YOURSELF AT HOME.

00:21.634 --> 00:22.965
Man:
HIS PRINTS WERE ON THE COUNTER.

00:22.967 --> 00:24.432
WELL, MR. DELAJAE SAYS
THAT HE WAS WITH YOU,

00:24.434 --> 00:26.865
WHEN THE SURVEILLANCE WAS TAKEN.
YOU SAY YES, HE'S FREE TO GO.

00:26.867 --> 00:28.832
A.J. CAME AND FOUND ME
AT SCHOOL.

00:28.834 --> 00:30.098
WHERE IS HE?

00:30.100 --> 00:31.832
HE TOOK OFF AND DIDN'T SAY
WHERE HE WAS GOING.

00:31.834 --> 00:34.632
YOU LIED TO THE POLICE
TO PROTECT YOUR SON.

00:34.634 --> 00:36.865
THIS HAS TO BE KEPT
IN THE FAMILY.

00:36.867 --> 00:38.765
I RECORDED HER SAYING IT.

00:38.767 --> 00:41.731
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

00:41.733 --> 00:44.998
IF YOU COULD SEE THIS HOUSE
THAT I'M LIVING IN RIGHT NOW.

00:45.000 --> 00:48.065
WHO WOULD GET IT NOW IF MAE
OR THE BISHOP WERE TO PASS ON?

00:48.067 --> 00:49.665
I REALLY HAVE NO IDEA.

00:49.667 --> 00:51.865
WELL,
MAYBE YOU SHOULD FIND OUT.

00:51.867 --> 00:54.732
I GOT US A ROOM
AT THE PEABODY.

00:54.734 --> 00:55.732
OH.

00:55.734 --> 00:57.765
HAVE YOU SENT THE FILE YET?

00:57.767 --> 00:59.431
NO, BUT I WAS
JUST ABOUT TO --

00:59.433 --> 01:01.965
WELL, DON'T. DON'T SEND IT.
DON'T.

01:01.967 --> 01:04.465
WHO IS IT?
WHO OWNS CITY ON A HILL?

01:04.467 --> 01:06.465
HARMONY & HOPE.

01:06.467 --> 01:15.098
♪♪

01:15.100 --> 01:16.298
IS THAT...

01:16.300 --> 01:18.032
FAITH, MM-HMM.

01:18.034 --> 01:20.965
SO PRETTY. SO SAD.

01:20.967 --> 01:23.232
SO...

01:23.234 --> 01:25.932
WHAT BRINGS YOU TO TOWN,
JUDEE?

01:25.934 --> 01:27.732
DIDN'T LIKE CHARITY'S
NEW ARRANGEMENT

01:27.734 --> 01:29.465
OF THE WELCOME SONG?

01:29.467 --> 01:33.865
SHE WAS JUST TRYING TO MAKE IT
MORE, YOU KNOW, CALVARY.

01:33.867 --> 01:35.999
AS IF HARMONY & HOPE
WOULD EVER

01:36.001 --> 01:39.332
MICROMANAGE
THINGS LIKE THAT.

01:39.334 --> 01:44.265
I'M HERE
BECAUSE YOU MET FERNANDO.

01:44.267 --> 01:47.665
I DID.
I DID MEET FERNANDO.

01:47.667 --> 01:50.198
MM.
IS HE NOT THE HANDSOMEST?

01:50.200 --> 01:51.465
HE IS.

01:51.467 --> 01:53.732
AND A GOOD ACTOR, TOO.

01:53.734 --> 01:55.265
I DIDN'T KNOW
HE WAS WITH H&H.

01:55.267 --> 01:57.132
AND NOW I DON'T KNOW

01:57.134 --> 02:01.732
WHY H&H HID FROM MY BROTHER
AND FROM ME AND CALVARY

02:01.734 --> 02:03.532
THAT THEY'RE BUYING UP
ALL THIS LAND.

02:03.534 --> 02:06.065
BOY, YOU MUST BE FUN
TO THROW A PARTY FOR.

02:06.067 --> 02:07.465
STOP TRYING TO PEEK OUT

02:07.467 --> 02:08.798
FROM UNDER THE BLINDFOLD
FOR A MINUTE.

02:08.800 --> 02:10.565
HOW ABOUT YOU STOP
BLINDFOLDING ME?

02:10.567 --> 02:14.798
WELL, WE WERE GOING TO
SURPRISE YOU.

02:14.800 --> 02:17.798
AND NOW THAT I'M GOING
TO LET YOU IN ON IT,

02:17.800 --> 02:19.798
I HOPE YOU DON'T SPOIL IT

02:19.800 --> 02:21.798
FOR THE REST
OF YOUR CONGREGATION,

02:21.800 --> 02:24.065
BECAUSE WE HOPE
TO ROLL IT OUT

02:24.067 --> 02:27.532
WHEN DADDY COMES TO VISIT
IN TWO WEEKS.

02:27.534 --> 02:29.332
ROLL OUT WHAT, JUDEE?

02:29.334 --> 02:32.798
I'M HERE TO MAKE A PRESENTATION
TO THE DEACON BOARD.

02:32.800 --> 02:35.299
WE WANT TO PUT CALVARY
ON THE MAP,

02:35.301 --> 02:37.965
BUILD IT INTO SOMETHING LIKE
SADDLEBACK, POTTER'S HOUSE.

02:37.967 --> 02:42.199
WE WANT TO MAKE THIS A CHURCH
WORTHY OF NATIONAL RESPECT.

02:42.201 --> 02:44.465
WE WANT TO BUILD
A BRAND-NEW COMMUNITY CENTER,

02:44.467 --> 02:47.199
TOP-OF-THE-LINE CHILDCARE
FACILITIES, MORE PARKING.

02:47.201 --> 02:51.398
A STATE-OF-THE-ART GYM
WITH STATE-OF-THE-ART TRAINERS

02:51.400 --> 02:53.532
WHO NOT ONLY TRAIN YOU,

02:53.534 --> 02:56.099
BUT THEY TELL YOU WHAT TO EAT
AND WHERE.

02:56.101 --> 03:00.565
AT ONE OF THE MAYBE
FIVE NEW RESTAURANTS.

03:00.567 --> 03:03.098
FIVE RESTAURANTS?
MM-HMM.

03:03.100 --> 03:04.799
SERIOUSLY?

03:07.334 --> 03:09.798
WELL, WHY SHOULD THESE
SOUL-FOOD SHACKS ON THE HIGHWAY

03:09.800 --> 03:12.131
BE GETTING ALL
OUR BELIEVERS' BENJAMINS?

03:12.133 --> 03:15.065
THIS IS WHAT WE HAVE BEEN
WORKING SO HARD

03:15.067 --> 03:16.732
TO SNATCH UP
ALL THAT LAND FOR.

03:16.734 --> 03:18.932
WE NEED SPACE TO DO THIS.

03:18.934 --> 03:21.332
AND IF THERE'S ENOUGH
LEFT IN THE BUDGET,

03:21.334 --> 03:24.532
WE MIGHT JUST DO
THE TABERNACLE, TOO.

03:24.534 --> 03:27.532
AND THIS WAS SUPPOSED
TO BE A SURPRISE?

03:27.534 --> 03:29.531
THAT WAS THE PLAN.

03:29.533 --> 03:31.465
SURPRISE!

03:31.467 --> 03:33.132
♪ AMEN ♪

03:35.601 --> 03:36.932
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

03:36.934 --> 03:38.198
♪ AMEN ♪

03:38.200 --> 03:41.132
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

03:41.134 --> 03:43.699
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

03:46.867 --> 03:48.165
♪ WELL ♪

03:51.667 --> 03:54.598
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

03:54.600 --> 04:00.132
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

04:00.134 --> 04:03.099
♪ AMEN, AMEN ♪
♪ OH ♪

04:06.600 --> 04:08.398
♪ YEAH ♪

04:08.400 --> 04:11.465
-- Captions by VITAC --
 www.vitac.com

04:11.467 --> 04:14.465
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

04:14.467 --> 04:18.465
♪♪

04:18.467 --> 04:20.432
I DON'T LIKE IT.

04:20.434 --> 04:22.865
I DON'T BELIEVE IT, AND I
DON'T LIKE IT. NOT ONE BIT.

04:22.867 --> 04:24.132
WELL, WHAT DON'T
YOU BELIEVE, BISHOP?

04:24.134 --> 04:26.732
BECAUSE THEY OWN
ALL THE LAND NOW.

04:26.734 --> 04:28.532
THE WHOLE CIRCLE
AROUND THE CHURCH.

04:28.534 --> 04:29.865
MOM.

04:29.867 --> 04:31.398
HOW COULD
YOU LET THAT HAPPEN?

04:31.400 --> 04:33.465
I DIDN'T KNOW THEY WERE H&H.

04:33.467 --> 04:35.065
FIRST TASHA SKANKS.

04:35.067 --> 04:36.665
AND NOW KERISSA.

04:36.667 --> 04:37.998
BUT HERE'S THE WEIRD PART,
THOUGH --

04:38.000 --> 04:40.598
I HATE TO SPEAK
AGAINST MY OWN SEX.

04:40.600 --> 04:42.932
BUT, SON, WHEN ARE YOU
GONNA STOP LETTING WOMEN

04:42.934 --> 04:45.032
LEAD YOU AROUND
LIKE A PONY ON A ROPE

04:45.034 --> 04:46.399
AT SOME SEEDY CARNIVAL?

04:46.401 --> 04:47.899
KERISSA SAID SHE DIDN'T KNOW.

04:47.901 --> 04:49.265
OH, KERISSA SAID.

04:49.267 --> 04:50.798
SHE WOULD SELL THE WATER

04:50.800 --> 04:52.665
FROM THAT LAKE OUT THERE
RIGHT UNDER MY EYES

04:52.667 --> 04:53.798
IF SHE THOUGHT IT WOULD
GIVE HER THE MONEY

04:53.800 --> 04:55.798
SHE NEEDED TO GET OUT OF HERE
AND INTO A HOUSE.

04:55.800 --> 04:56.998
James: GIGI.

04:57.000 --> 04:58.598
DID MS. WHITMORE
HAPPEN TO MENTION

04:58.600 --> 05:02.198
WHAT H&H WAS GOING TO EXPECT
IN RETURN FOR THIS BENEFICENCE?

05:02.200 --> 05:05.432
THAT'S WHAT I WAS GONNA SAY.
ODDLY ENOUGH, NO.

05:05.434 --> 05:09.132
BUT SHE DID SAY THAT THEY
WANTED NO CASH FROM THE CHURCH.

05:09.134 --> 05:10.998
THEY'RE
GONNA WANT SOMETHING.

05:11.000 --> 05:12.932
NOBODY
JUST GIVES MONEY AWAY.

05:12.934 --> 05:15.132
NOT ANYBODY WHO WANTS
TO RUN A CHURCH, ANYWAY.

05:15.134 --> 05:18.332
MM-HMM.
WELL...

05:18.334 --> 05:19.465
I COULD CALL BOB.

05:19.467 --> 05:21.365
HE'S NOT GONNA TELL YOU
THE TRUTH.

05:21.367 --> 05:23.832
MY GUESS IS, NO ONE
EVEN KNOWS THE TRUTH BUT HIM.

05:23.834 --> 05:26.098
NOT JUDEE. NOT PHIL.

05:26.100 --> 05:28.098
ISN'T THAT THE IMPRESSION
THAT YOU GET, GIGI?

05:28.100 --> 05:30.032
THEY DIDN'T SEEM
WELL-INFORMED. NO.

05:30.034 --> 05:31.598
UH, SPEAKING OF PHIL...

05:31.600 --> 05:34.299
ALL RIGHT, NOW, WHAT HAS
THAT GREASY NEGRO DONE NOW?

05:34.301 --> 05:37.032
WELL, IT'S NOT SO MUCH HIM
AS CHARITY.

05:37.034 --> 05:39.098
WHAT?
NO. LOOK.

05:39.100 --> 05:40.832
JACOB. MNH-MNH.

05:40.834 --> 05:42.398
ACCORDING TO HER,
THEY'RE IN LOVE.

05:42.400 --> 05:43.465
OH.

05:43.467 --> 05:45.265
AND THIS HAS BEEN
GOING ON FOR MONTHS.

05:48.567 --> 05:50.365
I THINK
I'M GONNA BE SICK.

05:50.367 --> 05:52.465
MAMA. REALLY? RIGHT NOW?
YOU HAD TO SAY THAT RIGHT NOW?

05:52.467 --> 05:54.265
MAMA.

05:54.267 --> 05:55.865
SOMEBODY SHOULD
HAVE TOLD THEM.

05:55.867 --> 05:58.132
I KNOW THAT I AM NOT AT
THE CENTER OF THE UNIVERSE,

05:58.134 --> 05:59.798
BUT YOUR SISTER'S CHOICE
IN MEN

05:59.800 --> 06:01.998
ALWAYS FEELS LIKE
SOME KIND OF PRECISION WEAPON

06:02.000 --> 06:04.198
DESIGNED SOLELY TO REMIND ME
WHAT A BAD JOB

06:04.200 --> 06:07.398
I DID AS A MOTHER,
AND IT GETS ME EVERY TIME.

06:07.400 --> 06:09.065
PHIL GROOMED HER FOR THIS,
MAMA.

06:09.067 --> 06:10.665
THIS ISN'T ON YOU.

06:10.667 --> 06:14.499
BUT IF SHE IS AVAILABLE
TO BE HOODWINKED THUS, THOUGH,

06:14.501 --> 06:17.098
I MEAN,
WHOSE FAULT IS THAT?

06:17.100 --> 06:21.798
FROM THE MOMENT A CHILD IS BORN,
IT PICKS UP SIGNALS.

06:21.800 --> 06:24.265
IT LEARNS HOW TO SEEK LOVE,
HOW TO GET ATTENTION.

06:24.267 --> 06:26.499
AND I MUST'VE JUST
BROKE HER INSTRUMENTS

06:26.501 --> 06:27.631
OR JAMMED THEM EARLY ON,

06:27.633 --> 06:29.765
BECAUSE THE GIRL
SEEKS UNHAPPINESS

06:29.767 --> 06:32.765
AND DISAPPOINTMENT
LIKE SHE WAS BRED IN SOME LAB

06:32.767 --> 06:34.432
TO DO IT.
MAYBE SHE WAS.

06:34.434 --> 06:35.898
I FEEL
THE SAME WAY ABOUT A.J.

06:35.900 --> 06:39.465
I WANT TO GO BACK IN TIME
JUST TO HOLD HIM,

06:39.467 --> 06:43.865
LOOK HIM IN HIS LITTLE EYES,
AND SAY, "I LOVE YOU."

06:43.867 --> 06:46.099
I AM SO SORRY,

06:46.101 --> 06:47.765
AND UNFORTUNATELY,

06:47.767 --> 06:50.632
BECAUSE WHAT YOUR FATHER AND I
WENT THROUGH WITH FAITH,

06:50.634 --> 06:53.432
I KNOW EXACTLY
HOW YOU FEEL.

06:53.434 --> 06:55.599
THANK YOU FOR SAYING SO.

06:55.601 --> 06:58.931
NOW, GRACE...
HMM?

06:58.933 --> 07:01.532
...WE HAVE TO HAVE
A MEETING WITH THE DEACONS

07:01.534 --> 07:04.265
TO CREATE SOME BULWARK
AGAINST THIS WAVE

07:04.267 --> 07:05.199
BEFORE IT HITS.

07:05.201 --> 07:07.132
DEFINITELY
BEFORE THEY VOTE.

07:07.134 --> 07:09.332
I CAN'T SET THAT MEETING,
MAMA.

07:09.334 --> 07:11.298
I HAVE TO BE
THE GOOD COP HERE.

07:11.300 --> 07:14.398
WELL, MAYBE IF WE THROW
SOME KIND

07:14.400 --> 07:17.198
OF
IMPROMPTU ENGAGEMENT PARTY

07:17.200 --> 07:20.665
TO CELEBRATE MY AND YOUR
FATHER'S INTENTION TO REMARRY,

07:20.667 --> 07:24.532
CERTAINLY THE BOARD
WOULD SHOW UP FOR THAT.

07:24.534 --> 07:26.998
ALL BUT CONNIE.
PROBABLY. YEAH.

07:27.000 --> 07:31.065
AND I DON'T SEE WHY A FEW
CAUTIONARY WORDS ABOUT THIS

07:31.067 --> 07:32.998
MIGHT BE DRIPPED
INTO WILLING EARS

07:33.000 --> 07:34.398
AMIDST
THE TINKLE OF FLUTES

07:34.400 --> 07:37.132
IN THE ROLL OF CONVERSATION.
DO YOU?

07:37.134 --> 07:40.665
AS LONG AS IT SEEMS LIKE I HAVE
NO IDEA YOU'RE GONNA DO IT.

07:40.667 --> 07:42.865
YEAH.
AND AS FAR AS CONNIE,

07:42.867 --> 07:47.031
THE WAY TO ENSURE HER PRESENCE
HERE IS TO NOT INVITE HER.

07:47.033 --> 07:50.965
OH, THE POOR THING CAN'T RESIST
A CHANCE TO BE RUDE.

07:50.967 --> 07:53.632
SHE THINKS IT MAKES
HER INTERESTING.

07:53.634 --> 07:56.865
AND, I DARESAY,
IT VERY NEARLY DOES.

07:56.867 --> 08:00.198
MAMA, WHO IS GONNA TALK
LIKE YOU WHEN YOU'RE GONE?

08:00.200 --> 08:02.465
NO ONE.

08:02.467 --> 08:04.831
HOW'D IT GO DOWN?

08:04.833 --> 08:08.565
YOU KNOW,
BETTER THAN USUAL.

08:08.567 --> 08:10.032
YOU OKAY?

08:10.034 --> 08:10.965
YEAH.

08:10.967 --> 08:13.132
I DO HAVE A QUESTION.

08:13.134 --> 08:14.798
ALL RIGHT, HIT ME.

08:14.800 --> 08:17.132
WELL, I JUST GOT OFF
THE PHONE WITH NADINE.

08:17.134 --> 08:19.998
WE DIDN'T GET THE HOUSE.
THEY TOOK A CASH OFFER.

08:20.000 --> 08:21.465
OH, SORRY.

08:21.467 --> 08:23.665
YEAH, ME TOO.

08:23.667 --> 08:26.798
BUT IT MADE ME WONDER
WHO WOULD GET THIS HOUSE

08:26.800 --> 08:28.265
WHEN YOUR PARENTS DIED.
DO YOU KNOW?

08:28.267 --> 08:29.998
SEE IF THEY'RE
GONNA LEAVE IT TO US?

08:30.000 --> 08:32.198
WELL, I WOULD NOT SAY NO
TO THAT. NO.

08:32.200 --> 08:35.598
BUT IF IT'S GONNA BE
LEFT TO YOU, GRACE, AND CHARITY,

08:35.600 --> 08:39.965
WHICH IT PROBABLY IS,
MAYBE THEY COULD BUY US OUT.

08:39.967 --> 08:41.699
I DON'T KNOW THEIR PLAN.

08:41.701 --> 08:44.098
WOULD YOU ASK?

08:44.100 --> 08:45.965
I DON'T REALLY WANT TO.

08:45.967 --> 08:47.299
[ SIGHS ]

08:47.301 --> 08:50.099
GREAT.
THANKS FOR YOUR HELP.

08:52.967 --> 08:55.198
I GOT A QUESTION
FOR YOU.

08:55.200 --> 08:57.165
WHAT?

08:57.167 --> 08:59.365
WHAT WERE YOU DOING
AT FERNANDO AMABLE'S OFFICE

08:59.367 --> 09:00.532
THE OTHER DAY?

09:05.333 --> 09:07.065
GETTING YOU CUFF LINKS.

09:07.067 --> 09:09.332
CUFF LINKS?
YEAH.

09:09.334 --> 09:11.398
YOU REMEMBER. HE HAD
THOSE CUFF LINKS THAT YOU LIKED.

09:11.400 --> 09:13.265
I STOPPED BY THERE TO SEE
IF HE COULD TELL ME

09:13.267 --> 09:14.732
WHERE I COULD GET SOME.

09:14.734 --> 09:17.465
I WAS THERE FOR YOU.

09:17.467 --> 09:19.765
NOW, WHY DID YOU THINK
I WAS THERE?

09:22.767 --> 09:24.632
I DON'T KNOW.
I DON'T KNOW.

09:26.900 --> 09:28.632
YOU KNOW,
I COULDN'T IMAGINE.

09:28.634 --> 09:31.265
OH, YOU COULD.
[ LAUGHS ]

09:31.267 --> 09:32.399
YOU COULD, AND YOU DID.

09:34.067 --> 09:37.065
BUT WHO ARE YOU?

09:37.067 --> 09:39.665
OFFICER GREENLEAF?

09:39.667 --> 09:44.332
SON OF INIQUITY,
JEZEBEL'S FAVORITE FOOL.

09:44.334 --> 09:46.665
WHO ARE YOU TO QUESTION ME

09:46.667 --> 09:49.198
AS IF I WAS SOME WHORE
ON THE STREET,

09:49.200 --> 09:51.132
FLAGGING DOWN CARS?
I NEVER --

09:51.134 --> 09:53.398
AFTER ALL...

09:53.400 --> 09:56.432
<i> ALL</i> OF THE PAIN
THAT YOU PUT ME THROUGH.

09:56.434 --> 09:58.865
WHERE WERE YOU?

09:58.867 --> 10:00.332
WHEN?

10:00.334 --> 10:05.099
THE DOZENS OF NIGHTS
THAT I SPENT ALONE IN OUR BED.

10:12.467 --> 10:14.365
♪ BOY, WHAT YOU LOOKING AT? ♪

10:14.367 --> 10:18.065
OKAY. SO, MY AUNTS
AND THEIR FRIEND REBECCA

10:18.067 --> 10:21.065
USED TO SING TOGETHER
IN THIS GROUP CALLED MYSTIQUE.

10:21.067 --> 10:23.065
WHAT? [ LAUGHS ]

10:23.067 --> 10:24.732
LOOKING LIKE
DESTINY'S CHILD.

10:24.734 --> 10:26.265
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

10:26.267 --> 10:27.932
THE VERSION
AFTER MICHELLE JOINED,

10:27.934 --> 10:30.332
BUT BEFORE BEY TOLD FARRAH
THEY WOULD SEND HER LUGGAGE.

10:30.334 --> 10:32.532
MM.
MM-HMM.

10:32.534 --> 10:34.665
-HEY, WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING?
-HEY.

10:34.667 --> 10:38.231
GRANDMA JUST ASKED US
TO PUT TOGETHER A SLIDESHOW,

10:38.233 --> 10:40.831
HAVE SOMETHING RUN
WHILE THE PARTY HAPPENS.

10:40.833 --> 10:42.731
SHE DIDN'T MENTIONED IT
TO ME.

10:42.733 --> 10:44.732
MAYBE SHE THOUGHT YOU WERE BUSY
WITH A.J.

10:44.734 --> 10:46.398
WHO'S A.J.?
HER BROTHER.

10:46.400 --> 10:47.532
WHAT'S HIS DEAL?

10:47.534 --> 10:50.065
NOTHING.

10:50.067 --> 10:52.798
IT WOULD'VE BEEN NICE TO THINK
ABOUT SOMETHING ELSE

10:52.800 --> 10:54.732
FOR A MINUTE,
ACTUALLY, BUT WHATEVER.

10:54.734 --> 10:56.765
FEEL FREE TO JOIN
IF YOU WANT.

10:58.867 --> 11:00.532
THANKS.

11:00.534 --> 11:03.598
OH, HAVE YOU SEEN THE ONE
WITH LADY MAE AND BISHOP

11:03.600 --> 11:05.465
AT THE PIE-EATING
CONTEST?

11:05.467 --> 11:07.132
SHOW HER.
OKAY.

11:07.134 --> 11:10.998
SHE WAS LOOKING AT HIM LIKE,
"BOY, IT'S TIME TO GO."

11:11.000 --> 11:12.798
OKAY, BUT, WAIT. LOOK AT THE GUY
IN THE BACK, TOO.

11:12.800 --> 11:14.198
OH, MY GOSH.
LOOK AT HIM!

11:14.200 --> 11:15.465
[ LAUGHS ]

11:15.467 --> 11:18.132
WHAT DO
YOU THINK OF THE PLAN?

11:20.500 --> 11:25.732
I THINK I WOULD HAVE APPRECIATED
IF I HEARD IT BEFORE GRACE.

11:25.734 --> 11:27.465
MAYBE EVEN BEFORE IT HAPPENED.

11:27.467 --> 11:28.932
DO I MATTER?

11:28.934 --> 11:32.732
PHIL, DON'T LET THIS CLOUD
YOUR THINKING.

11:32.734 --> 11:35.265
WHATEVER AGREEMENT
YOU HAVE MADE WITH DADDY,

11:35.267 --> 11:40.265
I'M SURE HE HAS
EVERY INTENTION OF HONORING.

11:40.267 --> 11:42.798
UH-HUH.

11:42.800 --> 11:45.131
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE
I DON'T KNOW?

11:45.133 --> 11:47.265
ANY PLANS FOR THE CHURCH

11:47.267 --> 11:51.465
OR FOR CALVARY'S PULPIT
YOU CAN SHARE?

11:51.467 --> 11:56.732
JUST THAT THINGS ARE GOING
TO KEEP PROGRESSING...

11:56.734 --> 12:00.465
AND YOU ARE APPRECIATED.

12:00.467 --> 12:03.665
BUT YOU KNOW THAT,
DON'T YOU?

12:03.667 --> 12:05.099
IF YOU DON'T, YOU SHOULD.

12:09.534 --> 12:11.532
APPRECIATED.

12:11.534 --> 12:21.032
♪♪

12:24.934 --> 12:27.732
WHY ARE YOU SLITHERING AROUND
BEHIND OUR BACKS

12:27.734 --> 12:29.998
WITH PHIL DEMARS?

12:30.000 --> 12:31.998
GIGI TOLD YOU?

12:32.000 --> 12:34.265
KNEW SHE WOULD.

12:34.267 --> 12:36.598
YOUR BROTHER AND SISTER
BOTH HAVE EXPRESSED A WORRY

12:36.600 --> 12:41.965
THAT PERHAPS YOU'RE
BEING TAKEN FOR A RIDE.

12:41.967 --> 12:43.232
I PRAY IT'S NOT SO.

12:43.234 --> 12:47.165
OKAY, SO, I CAN'T PREACH,
I CAN'T DATE.

12:47.167 --> 12:48.398
WHY HAVE
YOU KEPT IT A SECRET?

12:48.400 --> 12:49.632
IT'S LIKE Y'ALL
JUST WANT ME TO SIT ON

12:49.634 --> 12:51.165
SOME COUCH CUSHIONS
AND ROT.

12:51.167 --> 12:53.098
WHY HAVE YOU KEPT IT
A SECRET?

12:53.100 --> 12:54.898
BECAUSE I KNEW YOU WOULD
BE THIS WAY.

12:54.900 --> 12:56.132
THE WAY I'M BEING
HAS MORE TO DO

12:56.134 --> 12:58.598
WITH THE FACT
THAT YOU'VE KEPT IT A SECRET

12:58.600 --> 12:59.932
THAN IT HAS TO DO
WITH PHIL DEMARS.

12:59.934 --> 13:01.065
[ HAND POUNDS ]

13:01.067 --> 13:02.532
WHAT CAN YOU POSSIBLY
SEE IN THIS MAN?

13:02.534 --> 13:04.798
DADDY,
HE IS NOT WHAT YOU THINK.

13:04.800 --> 13:07.598
OH, REALLY?

13:07.600 --> 13:09.665
THEN WHAT IS HE?

13:09.667 --> 13:13.265
HE'S A LOT LIKE ME.
WE HAVE THE SAME VALUES.

13:13.267 --> 13:18.798
HE'S KIND,
HARDWORKING, CHASTE.

13:18.800 --> 13:21.132
HE KNOWS WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO BE ON A TEAM

13:21.134 --> 13:22.665
AND NEVER, EVER ASKED
TO BAT.

13:22.667 --> 13:25.065
[ LAUGHS ]
IN WHAT RESPECT?

13:27.334 --> 13:30.398
CAN YOU KEEP A SECRET?

13:30.400 --> 13:31.532
OH, MY GOD.

13:33.667 --> 13:36.965
I SHOULD SAY NO.

13:36.967 --> 13:42.332
DADDY, PHIL WRITES
EVERY SINGLE WORD

13:42.334 --> 13:44.665
THAT BOB WHITMORE SAYS
FROM PREACHING --

13:44.667 --> 13:47.032
HIS SERMONS, HIS BOOKS.

13:47.034 --> 13:48.899
IT'S PHIL.

13:48.901 --> 13:50.898
WHAT AM I TO MAKE OF THAT?

13:50.900 --> 13:53.832
I --

13:53.834 --> 13:57.132
IT SOUNDS LIKE HE'S NOT JUST
WOEFULLY AMBITIOUS --

13:57.134 --> 13:59.832
HE'S DUMB.
[ SIGHS ] WOW.

13:59.834 --> 14:03.065
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'M GONNA GO.

14:03.067 --> 14:04.865
I JUST DON'T WANT TO SEE
YOU HURT.

14:04.867 --> 14:07.732
THEN START BY NOT HURTING ME,
DADDY.

14:07.734 --> 14:13.465
START BY MAYBE ASKING ME
ABOUT THE MAN THAT --

14:13.467 --> 14:15.532
THAT I...

14:15.534 --> 14:17.265
LOVE?

14:17.267 --> 14:19.732
I KNOW IT'S FAST, DADDY,
BUT I DO.

14:19.734 --> 14:21.532
OH, CHARITY!
COME ON, NOW. LOVE?!

14:21.534 --> 14:23.632
JUST ASK TO MEET HIM!

14:25.467 --> 14:27.798
ASK LIKE YOU LIKE YOU CARE
MORE ABOUT ME

14:27.800 --> 14:29.765
THAN YOU DO
ABOUT BEING RIGHT.

14:31.934 --> 14:33.665
WOW.

14:33.667 --> 14:35.899
INVITE HIM TO THE PARTY.

14:40.134 --> 14:42.732
TELL HIM
I'LL GIVE HIM A CHANCE,

14:42.734 --> 14:47.999
BUT NO MORE THAN ANY MAN
WITH EYES ON MY DAUGHTER'S

14:48.001 --> 14:50.098
LIKELY TO GET.

14:50.100 --> 14:52.499
I'LL MAKE SURE
HE'S TERRIFIED.

14:55.600 --> 14:57.565
OH, YOU DO THAT.

15:00.667 --> 15:02.732
I JUST SPOKE WITH
MISTY WILLIAMS.

15:02.734 --> 15:06.265
AM I TO UNDERSTAND THERE'S
A PARTY TONIGHT AT THE MANSION?

15:06.267 --> 15:08.331
AN ENGAGEMENT PARTY.
YES, MA'AM.

15:08.333 --> 15:10.665
I ASSUME MY INVITATION
WAS TREATED AS JUNK.

15:10.667 --> 15:11.932
CAN YOU RESEND?

15:11.934 --> 15:13.665
OR I CAN PUT YOU DOWN
AS COMING.

15:13.667 --> 15:16.132
MM.
THAT'D BE SIMPLER.

15:16.134 --> 15:17.398
I'LL PUT YOU DOWN
AS COMING.

15:17.400 --> 15:18.532
THANK YOU.

15:18.534 --> 15:20.065
THANK<i> YOU</i>
FOR CATCHING IT.

15:20.067 --> 15:23.065
TA-TA.

15:23.067 --> 15:24.999
TO THE MINUTE.

15:27.734 --> 15:30.598
BISHOP, MAY I BOTHER YOU
FOR A SECOND?

15:30.600 --> 15:31.932
YOU MAY NOT.

15:31.934 --> 15:35.132
THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.
[ SCOFFS LIGHTLY ]

15:35.134 --> 15:38.398
WELL, YOU KNOW THAT ZORA'S
DOING THIS PRESENTATION

15:38.400 --> 15:39.565
FOR THE PARTY.
MM.

15:39.567 --> 15:41.299
A ROMANTIC MONTAGE.

15:41.301 --> 15:42.898
WELL, SHE'S RAIDED
MY PHOTO ALBUM

15:42.900 --> 15:44.765
AND EVERYBODY ELSE'S,
I THINK.

15:44.767 --> 15:46.699
WHAT DOES SHE WANT NOW --
MY BLOOD TYPE?

15:46.701 --> 15:49.232
NO, YOUR MARRIAGE LICENSE.

15:49.234 --> 15:51.232
SHE ASKED ME FOR IT, BUT I HAVE
NO IDEA WHERE YOU AND MAE

15:51.234 --> 15:54.232
KEEP THOSE KINDS OF IMPORTANT
PAPERS -- DEEDS AND WILLS.

15:54.234 --> 15:58.465
IT MUST BE UPSTAIRS
IN THE SAFE IN MY CLOSET.

15:58.467 --> 16:01.265
I JUST HOPE I REMEMBER
THE COMBINATION.

16:01.267 --> 16:02.932
YOU CAN WAIT RIGHT HERE.

16:02.934 --> 16:05.065
OH, NO, IT'S OKAY.
I'M NOT BUSY.

16:05.067 --> 16:06.398
OKAY.

16:06.400 --> 16:12.532
♪♪

16:12.534 --> 16:13.598
OKAY.

16:13.600 --> 16:17.732
♪♪

16:17.734 --> 16:20.732
SO, YOU KEEP EVERYTHING
IN THERE?

16:20.734 --> 16:23.198
SINCE MAC DIED, YES.

16:23.200 --> 16:27.398
WE USED TO HAVE
A SAFETY DEPOSIT BOX IN TOWN,

16:27.400 --> 16:29.599
BUT SINCE THEY
FORCED ME TO RETIRE,

16:29.601 --> 16:31.932
I HAVE TOO LITTLE REASON
TO GO THERE.

16:31.934 --> 16:33.465
MM.

16:33.467 --> 16:36.065
YOU AND JACOB COULD KEEP YOUR
PAPERS IN HERE, IF YOU LIKE.

16:36.067 --> 16:38.532
OH, I'LL TALK TO JACOB
ABOUT THAT.

16:38.534 --> 16:40.265
THANK YOU SO MUCH
FOR OFFERING.

16:40.267 --> 16:42.532
OF COURSE. WE'RE FAMILY.

16:42.534 --> 16:49.332
I'D HATE TO SEE ANYTHING LOST
BY A FLOOD, FIRE, OR ACT OF GOD.

16:49.334 --> 16:51.998
AH! AH.

16:52.000 --> 16:55.065
THERE IT IS!
[ LAUGHS ]

16:55.067 --> 16:56.265
[ SIGHS ]

16:56.267 --> 16:58.799
AH, STEEL TRAP.

16:58.801 --> 17:00.665
IN WHAT SENSE, BISHOP?

17:00.667 --> 17:02.265
WELL, MY MIND
HAS STILL GOT IT.

17:02.267 --> 17:04.665
[ Chuckling ] OH.

17:04.667 --> 17:06.932
MM...OKAY.

17:06.934 --> 17:08.298
SO, YOUR WILL
IS IN THAT MESS?

17:08.300 --> 17:09.498
IT IS.

17:09.500 --> 17:12.598
I DON'T LIKE TO GIVE THINGS
LIKE THIS TOO MUCH RESPECT.

17:12.600 --> 17:17.532
WE GUARD THEM WITH LOCK
AND KEY OUR WHOLE LIVES,

17:17.534 --> 17:21.731
AND MOST OF THEM
MEAN ALMOST NOTHING

17:21.733 --> 17:23.531
WITHIN FIVE MINUTES
AFTER WE'RE DEAD.

17:23.533 --> 17:24.832
HERE IT IS.

17:24.834 --> 17:28.465
AH, WOULD YOU LOOK AT THAT!
THANK YOU.

17:32.834 --> 17:35.098
OH, ANYTHING ELSE?

17:35.100 --> 17:37.665
NO, NOT RIGHT NOW.
THANKS.

17:37.667 --> 17:39.065
MM-HMM.

17:39.067 --> 17:41.798
ONE THING -- YOU HANDLE
THAT RELIC WITH CARE, NOW.

17:41.800 --> 17:43.931
I MAY BE PHILOSOPHICAL,

17:43.933 --> 17:46.231
BUT YOU KNOW HOW MAE
GETS ABOUT THESE THINGS.

17:46.233 --> 17:48.165
OH, YES, I CERTAINLY DO.

17:58.100 --> 17:59.565
OH!

17:59.567 --> 18:02.398
SO, WHAT WERE THE TWO
OF YOU DOING IN HERE?

18:02.400 --> 18:05.865
OH, KERISSA WANTED
OUR MARRIAGE LICENSE

18:05.867 --> 18:09.631
FOR ZORA'S LITTLE
AUDIOVISUAL EXTRAVAGANZA.

18:09.633 --> 18:11.299
OH, SHE DID, DID SHE?

18:11.301 --> 18:13.098
THAT'S FASCINATING.

18:13.100 --> 18:15.599
I KNOW YOU KERISSA HAVE HAD
YOUR DIFFERENCES,

18:15.601 --> 18:18.065
BUT IT'S MORE APPARENT
TO ME THAN USUAL

18:18.067 --> 18:22.598
THAT, WELL,
FAMILY IS EVERYTHING.

18:22.600 --> 18:24.932
OH, IT IS, ISN'T IT?

18:24.934 --> 18:26.532
YOU CAN'T ESCAPE IT.

18:26.534 --> 18:28.798
OH! AND, WELL,
HOW WOULD YOU FEEL

18:28.800 --> 18:32.532
ABOUT HAVING LUNCH
WITH ME DOWNSTAIRS, BELOVED?

18:32.534 --> 18:34.532
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

18:34.534 --> 18:41.365
♪♪

18:44.267 --> 18:46.265
WHAT'S GOING ON?

18:46.267 --> 18:48.465
MAMA AND DADDY ARE
HAVING A PARTY TONIGHT,

18:48.467 --> 18:50.965
AND THEY WANT YOU
TO COME.

18:50.967 --> 18:52.365
AS WHAT?

18:52.367 --> 18:54.598
AS SOMEONE
I LIKE VERY MUCH.

18:54.600 --> 18:57.065
AND I'VE EXPLAINED.

18:57.067 --> 18:59.332
SO THEY KNOW NOW?
ABOUT US?

18:59.334 --> 19:00.865
THEY DO.

19:00.867 --> 19:02.998
AND HOW HAVE
THEY TAKEN IT?

19:03.000 --> 19:05.399
THEY'RE WILLING TO LET YOU
COME TO THE HOUSE --

19:05.401 --> 19:07.265
TO THEIR ENGAGEMENT PARTY,
PHIL.

19:07.267 --> 19:09.132
IT'S SOMETHING.

19:09.134 --> 19:12.032
WHAT?
YOU DON'T WANT TO COME?

19:12.034 --> 19:15.032
CHARITY,
YOU KNOW HOW I FEEL.

19:15.034 --> 19:17.031
BUT DO YOU KNOW
HOW<i> I</i> FEEL?

19:17.033 --> 19:19.399
DO YOU KNOW THAT I AM
TRYING TO MAKE THIS WORK?

19:19.401 --> 19:20.999
FOR<i> YOU.</i>

19:21.001 --> 19:23.265
MEANWHILE, I'M FORBIDDEN
FROM USING THE RECORDING

19:23.267 --> 19:24.499
YOU GAVE ME OF GRACE.

19:24.501 --> 19:26.698
JUDEE IS GIVING ME
THE RUNAROUND.

19:26.700 --> 19:29.498
ABOUT WHAT?

19:29.500 --> 19:31.899
NOTHING.

19:31.901 --> 19:34.499
I'M WORRIED THAT ALL
I'M GONNA END UP WITH

19:34.501 --> 19:36.031
AT THE END OF THIS IS...

19:36.033 --> 19:37.465
A GIRLFRIEND AND...

19:37.467 --> 19:40.731
OH, WELL, IF I'M NOT ENOUGH
OF A FINISH LINE FOR YOU,

19:40.733 --> 19:41.798
CUT ME LOOSE.

19:41.800 --> 19:44.265
OH, NO,
THAT'S NOT WHAT I MEANT.

19:44.267 --> 19:46.732
IT'S JUST...

19:46.734 --> 19:48.465
[ SIGHS ]

19:50.800 --> 19:54.265
WHAT TIME
SHOULD I BE THERE?

19:54.267 --> 19:55.299
7:00.
GREAT.

19:55.301 --> 19:57.031
MM.
LOOKING FORWARD TO IT.

19:57.033 --> 19:58.632
MM-HMM.

19:58.634 --> 20:04.298
♪♪

20:04.300 --> 20:06.131
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

20:06.133 --> 20:08.532
AH. HOWDY, PASTOR.

20:08.534 --> 20:09.865
MORE SURPRISES?

20:09.867 --> 20:11.798
<i> YOU</i> TELL<i> ME.</i>

20:11.800 --> 20:13.998
I WAS JUST IN YOUR CUTE
LITTLE MEDIA OFFICE

20:14.000 --> 20:16.598
CHECKING OUT THE PROJECTOR
FOR THE DEACON BOARD MEETING

20:16.600 --> 20:20.132
AND I WAS TOLD TO BE SURE
AND HAVE IT BACK BEFORE 4:00,

20:20.134 --> 20:22.831
BECAUSE SOMEONE IS
HAVING A PARTY TONIGHT.

20:22.833 --> 20:24.298
YEAH,
THAT WOULD BE MY PARENTS.

20:24.300 --> 20:26.999
WHAT KIND OF PARTY,
PRAY TELL?

20:27.001 --> 20:28.165
AN ENGAGEMENT PARTY.

20:28.167 --> 20:29.831
AS IN
"RULES OF ENGAGEMENT"?

20:29.833 --> 20:32.365
AS IN RE-ENGAGEMENT, ACTUALLY.
WHY?

20:37.534 --> 20:39.499
DID YOU TELL YOUR PARENTS
ABOUT OUR TALK?

20:39.501 --> 20:41.565
OUR PLANS FOR CALVARY?

20:44.800 --> 20:46.099
I DID.

20:46.101 --> 20:48.365
AND YOU DON'T THINK THIS PARTY
IS JUST A CHANCE FOR THEM

20:48.367 --> 20:50.765
TO SPEW VENOM ABOUT IT
IN FRONT OF THE DEACONS?

20:50.767 --> 20:53.732
I THINK
IT'S JUST A PARTY.

20:53.734 --> 20:56.298
THEN INVITE ME.

20:56.300 --> 20:58.832
GREAT.

20:58.834 --> 21:02.031
YOU CAN BE MY PLUS-1.

21:02.033 --> 21:05.031
IT'LL BE MY PLEASURE.

21:05.033 --> 21:07.065
♪♪

21:07.067 --> 21:09.465
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:09.467 --> 21:11.465
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

21:11.467 --> 21:14.865
THAT MAKES ONE OF US.

21:14.867 --> 21:16.131
Jacob: YEAH.
THIS PLACE IS GREAT.

21:16.133 --> 21:18.198
YEAH, MAN, IT'S COMING TOGETHER.
DOPE.

21:18.200 --> 21:19.665
YEAH,
NIKKI AIN'T GOT NO SENSE,

21:19.667 --> 21:21.598
BUT SHE HAS HER SOME TASTES,
THAT'S FOR SURE.

21:21.600 --> 21:22.798
[ LAUGHS ]

21:22.800 --> 21:25.398
SO, WHAT'D YOU WANT
TO TALK TO ME ABOUT?

21:25.400 --> 21:29.532
WELL, I KNOW WE'RE NO LONGER
OFFICIALLY IN BUSINESS.

21:29.534 --> 21:30.732
YEAH,
I'M SORRY ABOUT THAT.

21:30.734 --> 21:32.398
NO PROBLEM.

21:32.400 --> 21:36.665
BUT I GOT A LITTLE IDEA THAT
I THINK WOULD BE GOOD FOR YOU.

21:36.667 --> 21:39.265
I THINK IT'LL GET YOU AROUND
THIS WHOLE APOLOGY THING

21:39.267 --> 21:40.732
THAT I HEAR THE TEAM'S
BEEN ASKING YOU FOR.

21:40.734 --> 21:43.132
[ LAUGHS ] ALL RIGHT.

21:46.134 --> 21:50.932
SO, REMEMBER WHEN LeBRON
STARTED THAT SCHOOL BACK

21:50.934 --> 21:52.998
IN HIS HOMETOWN --
I PROMISE?

21:53.000 --> 21:54.932
YEAH, YEAH, YEAH,
HE GOT MAD LOVE FOR THAT.

21:54.934 --> 21:56.665
SO, HOW ABOUT YOU DO
SOMETHING LIKE THAT HERE?

21:56.667 --> 21:57.932
OKAY.

21:57.934 --> 22:01.298
EXCEPT FOR A SCHOOL
THAT'S ALREADY IN OPERATION.

22:01.300 --> 22:03.498
OKAY, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.
WHAT SCHOOL?

22:03.500 --> 22:04.832
ANY SCHOOL.

22:04.834 --> 22:06.965
OR EXCELLENCE.

22:09.334 --> 22:11.732
EXCELLENCE?
RIGHT.

22:11.734 --> 22:13.332
THAT'S YOUR WIFE'S SCHOOL.

22:13.334 --> 22:15.465
IT IS.
EXCELLENCE ACADEMY.

22:15.467 --> 22:17.732
SO YOU WANT ME
TO GIVE THEM MONEY?

22:17.734 --> 22:20.732
WELL, I WANT YOU TO GET
YOURSELF OFF THAT BENCH

22:20.734 --> 22:21.932
WITHOUT SACRIFICING
YOUR VALUES.

22:21.934 --> 22:24.398
IS THAT WHY YOU CALLED ME
HERE TODAY?

22:24.400 --> 22:27.065
THAT'S THE FAVOR
YOU WANT TO DO FOR ME?

22:27.067 --> 22:28.798
WELL, I MEAN, YOU KNOW,
IF IT'S...

22:28.800 --> 22:30.265
IF IT MAKES SENSE.

22:30.267 --> 22:31.465
YEAH.

22:31.467 --> 22:33.798
I THOUGHT
YOU WERE DIFFERENT, MAN.

22:33.800 --> 22:34.865
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"DIFFERENT"?

22:34.867 --> 22:36.398
HOLD ON. DANTE.

22:36.400 --> 22:37.865
HOLD UP, MAN.
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

22:37.867 --> 22:40.365
FOR WHAT, MAN? WHY?

22:40.367 --> 22:42.665
HOLD UP FOR WHAT?

22:42.667 --> 22:44.598
LOOK, I'M SORRY,
ALL RIGHT?

22:44.600 --> 22:46.732
I WAS JUST TRYING

22:46.734 --> 22:48.865
TO GET MYSELF OUT OF TROUBLE
WITH ME AND THE WIFE.

22:48.867 --> 22:49.998
I THOUGHT THIS COULD
BE A GOOD IDEA.

22:50.000 --> 22:51.332
YEAH, IT'D BE GOOD
FOR EVERYBODY, RIGHT?

22:51.334 --> 22:52.532
YEAH.

22:52.534 --> 22:54.798
NAH. THERE'S NO SUCH THING.
YOU SEE, MAN,

22:54.800 --> 22:57.732
YOU'RE JUST LIKE NIKKI
AND CAMERON AND ALL OF THEM.

22:57.734 --> 23:00.632
ALL I SEE ARE HANDS, MAN.

23:00.634 --> 23:03.165
I WAS GONNA SIT DOWN THERE
AND PRAY WITH YOU, TOO.

23:03.167 --> 23:05.232
[ SCOFFS ] DAMN.

23:07.133 --> 23:08.932
COME -- DANTE.

23:11.667 --> 23:12.932
Judee: SO, YOUR CHURCH FAMILY

23:12.934 --> 23:16.631
CAN BE INCORPORATED
INTO EVERY AVENUE.

23:16.633 --> 23:20.765
AND THERE SHE BLOWS.
[ LAUGHS ]

23:20.767 --> 23:22.231
ANY QUESTIONS?

23:22.233 --> 23:25.965
[ CHUCKLES ] HOW WILL
ALL OF THIS BE FUNDED?

23:25.967 --> 23:28.365
NOT WITH CASH
FROM CALVARY.

23:28.367 --> 23:32.498
NO, DADDY MADE SURE BEFORE
WE STARTED DOWN THIS PATH

23:32.500 --> 23:35.765
THAT THERE WOULD BE
NO CASH EXCHANGE.

23:35.767 --> 23:40.532
HARMONY & HOPE IS PREPARED
TO PAY FOR THE ENTIRE PROJECT.

23:40.534 --> 23:43.132
ALL WE WANT ARE A FEW SEATS
ON THE BOARD

23:43.134 --> 23:44.865
AND A CHANCE TO BE
PART OF THE CONVO.

23:44.867 --> 23:46.665
HOW MANY SEATS
ARE WE TALKING?

23:46.667 --> 23:47.998
50%.

23:48.000 --> 23:50.198
WHO AMONG US
IS SUPPOSED TO QUIT?

23:50.200 --> 23:54.798
NOBODY. NO, DID YOU NOT
LOOK AT THIS PICTURE?

23:54.800 --> 23:56.598
THIS CHURCH IS GONNA GROW.

23:56.600 --> 24:01.098
WE WANT 12 NEW SEATS
AS WE GROW.

24:01.100 --> 24:03.965
SO 12 AND 12,
HALF AND HALF, 50%.

24:05.867 --> 24:07.732
THANKS FOR TAKING THE TIME,
JUDEE.

24:07.734 --> 24:08.865
OF COURSE.

24:08.867 --> 24:11.565
AND Y'ALL TAKE YOURS, TOO.

24:11.567 --> 24:14.365
YOU KNOW,
WITHIN REASON, OBVIOUSLY.

24:14.367 --> 24:15.832
WHEN DO YOU NEED AN ANSWER?

24:15.834 --> 24:17.698
DADDY'S COMING TO TOWN
IN TWO WEEKS.

24:17.700 --> 24:20.598
WE WOULD LOVE
TO ANNOUNCE IT THEN.

24:20.600 --> 24:23.465
OR NOT.
WHATEVER YOU DECIDE.

24:23.467 --> 24:25.098
GOT IT.

24:25.100 --> 24:26.765
WE'LL CONFER.

24:26.767 --> 24:29.865
THANK YOU.
-THANK YOU.

24:34.233 --> 24:37.232
WE'LL LET YOU FOLKS TALK.

24:42.867 --> 24:44.332
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

24:46.334 --> 24:49.332
I WOULD LOVE TO FIND
A WAY TO DO THIS.

24:49.334 --> 24:53.165
SO, HOW DO WE THINK
THAT WENT?

24:53.167 --> 24:54.998
50% IS A LOT TO ASK, JUDEE.

24:55.000 --> 24:56.265
FOR WHAT WE'LL
ACTUALLY SPEND,

24:56.267 --> 24:59.465
GRACE, THEY SHOULD GIVE US
COMPLETE CONTROL.

24:59.467 --> 25:00.732
THEY WILL NEVER GO
FOR THAT.

25:00.734 --> 25:02.465
YOU SURE?

25:02.467 --> 25:05.065
I'M SURE
I WON'T LET THEM.

25:05.067 --> 25:07.632
WELL, WHOSE SIDE
ARE YOU ON, GRACE?

25:07.634 --> 25:10.032
I'M ON GOD'S, I HOPE, JUDEE.

25:10.034 --> 25:11.399
US TOO.

25:13.200 --> 25:15.732
I'LL SEE YOU AT THE PARTY.

25:15.734 --> 25:17.132
HMM?

25:17.134 --> 25:23.265
♪♪

25:23.267 --> 25:26.732
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

25:26.734 --> 25:30.665
♪♪

25:34.267 --> 25:36.998
♪♪

25:37.000 --> 25:40.899
CLARA. [ LAUGHS ]
YOU MADE IT.

25:40.901 --> 25:44.432
YOU WERE AT OUR FIRST ENGAGEMENT
PARTY, IF I RECALL CORRECTLY.

25:44.434 --> 25:48.065
I WAS, AND THIS BETTER
BE THE LAST.

25:48.067 --> 25:49.865
OH, YOU KNOW IT WILL BE.

25:49.867 --> 25:51.198
WOULD YOU ALL EXCUSE ME
A SECOND?

25:51.200 --> 25:53.798
MM-HMM.

25:53.800 --> 25:56.398
MR. DEMARS.

25:56.400 --> 25:59.798
I UNDERSTAND YOU AND I
MIGHT HAVE A REASON

25:59.800 --> 26:01.665
TO SETTLE
OUR LITTLE FEUD.

26:01.667 --> 26:03.532
OH, I'VE NEVER FELT
IT WAS A FEUD AS MUCH

26:03.534 --> 26:05.598
AS A FRIENDLY DISAGREEMENT.

26:05.600 --> 26:07.998
WELL, WE WON'T ARGUE
ABOUT THAT NOW, WILL WE?

26:08.000 --> 26:09.932
LET'S GET YOU
A LITTLE SOMETHING.

26:12.667 --> 26:14.398
LOOK AT THAT.

26:14.400 --> 26:16.265
THEY ALMOST LOOK
FRIENDLY.

26:16.267 --> 26:17.732
YOU'RE
A MIRACLE WORKER.

26:17.734 --> 26:20.998
MM, DON'T BUDDY UP TO ME.

26:21.000 --> 26:23.865
CHARITY, THE MISSION WAS TO
GET BACK THE CHURCH

26:23.867 --> 26:25.065
FROM HARMONY & HOPE.

26:25.067 --> 26:26.865
YOU ARE LITERALLY
IN BED WITH THEM.

26:26.867 --> 26:29.132
WELL, WE ARE NOT LIKE THAT.
OH.

26:29.134 --> 26:30.998
AND IF ANYTHING IS GONNA
UNDO THE MISSION,

26:31.000 --> 26:33.599
IT'S THE WAY YOU MISHANDLED
THAT SON OF YOURS.

26:33.601 --> 26:36.065
IF ANYBODY KNEW
WHAT YOU'VE DONE,

26:36.067 --> 26:37.998
WE'D ALREADY BE OUT
ON OUR ASSES.

26:38.000 --> 26:40.932
OKAY, JUST SO I'M CLEAR,
WHAT EXACTLY HAVE I DONE?

26:40.934 --> 26:43.532
OH!
"WHAT EXACTLY HAVE I DONE?"

26:43.534 --> 26:45.732
YOU LIED TO THE POLICE
TO GIVE HIM AN ALIBI.

26:45.734 --> 26:48.532
BUT AM I SCREAMING THAT
FROM THE ROOFTOPS? NO.

26:48.534 --> 26:49.998
BUT DO I GET
ANY CREDIT FOR THAT?

26:50.000 --> 26:51.265
NO.

26:51.267 --> 26:53.665
ALL I GET IS SNITCHED ON
FOR DOING THE ONE THING

26:53.667 --> 26:55.965
THAT AIN'T GOT NOTHING TO DO
WITH ANY OF THIS --

26:55.967 --> 26:58.565
FALLING IN LOVE.

26:58.567 --> 26:59.699
YOU'RE SOMETHING ELSE,
GRACE.

26:59.701 --> 27:02.499
REALLY, YOU ARE [LAUGHS]
SOMETHING ELSE.

27:04.500 --> 27:07.198
THEY SLOWLY TAKE CONTROL
OF THE CHURCH.

27:07.200 --> 27:09.132
BUT WE STILL HAVE
HALF THE SEATS.

27:09.134 --> 27:11.398
YES, BUT IF THEY GET
THOSE 12 SEATS,

27:11.400 --> 27:14.532
WHO WILL THOSE
12 PEOPLE BE ANYHOW?

27:14.534 --> 27:17.865
ALL THEY NEED IS
TO WRANGLE ONE MORE VOTE

27:17.867 --> 27:19.532
OUT OF SOME FOOL
LIKE CONNIE,

27:19.534 --> 27:22.232
AND THEN THEY CAN DO
WHATEVER THEY WANT.

27:22.234 --> 27:24.199
MM.
WELL, THAT'S NOT GOOD.

27:24.201 --> 27:25.598
OH, YOU THINK?

27:25.600 --> 27:27.332
CONNIE IS WRONG
ABOUT THESE PEOPLE,

27:27.334 --> 27:29.332
AND SHE HAS BEEN
FROM THE START.

27:29.334 --> 27:30.932
DON'T LET THE NEWS FOR YOU,
MISS CLARA.

27:30.934 --> 27:32.798
DANTE WAS DOING
GOD'S WORK.

27:32.800 --> 27:34.998
YEAH, AND YOU KNOW
THEY'RE ALWAYS TRYING TO PAINT

27:35.000 --> 27:36.398
THE BLACK MAN
AS THE AGGRESSOR.

27:36.400 --> 27:38.798
LOOK, WE HAVE TO STAND
FOR SOMETHING,

27:38.800 --> 27:40.465
OR WE'LL FALL FOR ANYTHING.

27:40.467 --> 27:42.198
MY MAN MALCOLM X
SAID THAT.

27:42.200 --> 27:45.398
OH, WELL,
I KNOW WHO SAID THAT.

27:45.400 --> 27:48.365
I KNEW WHO SAID THAT
BEFORE YOU WERE EVEN BORN.

27:50.400 --> 27:51.998
HI, MS. JACKSON.
HOW ARE YOU?

27:52.000 --> 27:54.532
I'M WELL, THANK YOU.
AND YOU ARE?

27:54.534 --> 27:56.532
THAT'S SOPHIA,
GRACE'S DAUGHTER.

27:58.600 --> 28:01.065
OH, MY GOODNESS,
YOU ARE SOPHIA, AREN'T YOU?

28:01.067 --> 28:03.598
I THOUGHT YOU WERE SOPHIA.
OH, NO.

28:03.600 --> 28:06.565
I WAS WONDERING HOW YOU KEPT
THIS ROMANCE

28:06.567 --> 28:08.865
GOING WHILE YOU WERE AWAY
AT SCHOOL.

28:08.867 --> 28:10.931
NOW IT ALL MAKES SENSE.

28:10.933 --> 28:12.732
[ LAUGHTER ]

28:12.734 --> 28:20.198
♪♪

28:20.200 --> 28:27.198
♪♪

28:27.200 --> 28:30.465
SO, WHAT ARE
YOUR INTENTIONS?

28:30.467 --> 28:33.532
AT THIS POINT, KEEP ON
GETTING TO KNOW HER

28:33.534 --> 28:36.332
AND SEE WHERE IT GOES.

28:36.334 --> 28:40.665
YOU HAVE
NO ULTERIOR MOTIVES?

28:40.667 --> 28:42.532
BISHOP, MY ANTIPATHY
FOR YOUR FAMILY

28:42.534 --> 28:45.532
AND THE HAVOC IT'S WREAKED
ON CALVARY IS A WELL-KNOWN FACT.

28:45.534 --> 28:49.598
WELL,
THAT'S PARTLY WHY I ASK.

28:49.600 --> 28:53.665
SO YOUR DAUGHTER MUST
REALLY BE SOMETHING SPECIAL

28:53.667 --> 28:54.932
TO KNOCK ME OFF MY HORSE

28:54.934 --> 28:58.465
AND RISK BECOMING PART
OF YOUR FAMILY.

28:58.467 --> 29:00.465
WOULDN'T YOU SAY?

29:00.467 --> 29:02.931
[ LAUGHS ]

29:02.933 --> 29:08.865
♪♪

29:08.867 --> 29:11.132
HEY.

29:11.134 --> 29:16.132
PASTOR DEMARS, MIGHT I HAVE
A MOMENT ALONE WITH MY FIANCé?

29:16.134 --> 29:18.332
"FIANCé." OH, I LIKE
THE SOUND OF THAT.

29:18.334 --> 29:19.532
OF COURSE.

29:19.534 --> 29:21.998
BISHOP, IF YOU HAVE
ANY MORE QUESTIONS...

29:22.000 --> 29:23.831
I'LL FIND YOU. AMEN?

29:23.833 --> 29:25.365
AMEN.

29:25.367 --> 29:32.665
♪♪

29:32.667 --> 29:34.865
SO, WHAT IS THE VERDICT?

29:34.867 --> 29:39.931
WELL, HE'S EITHER INSINCERE
AND UNCONVINCING

29:39.933 --> 29:42.598
OR SINCERE
AND UTTERLY UNFEELING.

29:42.600 --> 29:46.165
EITHER WAY,
I'D NEVER GIVE MY BLESSING.

29:48.467 --> 29:51.499
HE DIDN'T SAY THE ONE THING
THAT WOULD HAVE WORKED.

29:51.501 --> 29:53.431
I KNOW.
OFFER TO QUIT HIS JOB.

29:53.433 --> 29:55.632
EXACTLY. AS FAR AS
I'M CONCERNED,

29:55.634 --> 29:58.765
ANYTHING SHORT OF THAT IN
THIS SITUATION IS INSUFFICIENT.

29:58.767 --> 30:01.532
AND SO UNFORTUNATE.

30:01.534 --> 30:02.965
HOW DID IT GO
WITH DADDY?

30:02.967 --> 30:05.032
AS WELL AS IT COULD.

30:05.034 --> 30:07.132
I SAW YOU
ARGUING WITH GRACE.

30:07.134 --> 30:09.265
WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?
YOU AND ME?

30:09.267 --> 30:11.865
WHO CARES? SHE THINKS
SHE'S JUDGE AND JURY.

30:11.867 --> 30:14.732
IT NEVER OCCURS TO HER
THAT SHE'S THE ACCUSED.

30:14.734 --> 30:16.932
READY TO LET ME
SEND THE RECORDING?

30:16.934 --> 30:20.398
NO. I STILL WORRY ABOUT
THE EFFECT IT'LL HAVE

30:20.400 --> 30:22.332
ON THAT POOR SON OF HERS.

30:22.334 --> 30:24.065
BUT I DO NEED
MORE CHAMPAGNE.

30:24.067 --> 30:26.398
WOULD YOU BE SO KIND
AS TO ACCOMPANY ME

30:26.400 --> 30:28.465
TO THE BEVERAGE STATION?

30:28.467 --> 30:29.865
LET ME SEE
HOW JUDEE'S DOING.

30:29.867 --> 30:31.798
I KNOW SHE'S GRACE'S GUEST,

30:31.800 --> 30:33.665
BUT SHE'S LOOKING
A LITTLE DESERTED TO ME.

30:33.667 --> 30:35.899
FINE.

30:35.901 --> 30:38.098
BUT DON'T BE LONG.

30:38.100 --> 30:46.165
♪♪

30:46.167 --> 30:49.398
MM.

30:49.400 --> 30:50.932
FRATERNIZING
WITH THE LOCALS?

30:50.934 --> 30:53.699
IT'S DIFFERENT WITH HER.

30:56.167 --> 30:58.232
LIKE IT WAS WITH ME?

30:58.234 --> 30:59.965
OH, THAT'S RIGHT.

30:59.967 --> 31:02.132
WE DON'T TALK ABOUT THAT.

31:02.134 --> 31:04.032
I FORGOT.
[ SPOON CLINKING ]

31:04.034 --> 31:05.565
James:
GATHER 'ROUND, EVERYBODY.

31:05.567 --> 31:07.332
WOULD YOU ACCOMPANY ME?

31:07.334 --> 31:08.899
ATTENTION, EVERYBODY.

31:13.267 --> 31:16.431
FIRST, I WANT TO THANK YOU ALL
FOR JOINING US

31:16.433 --> 31:17.765
ON THIS VERY MOMENTOUS EVENING.

31:17.767 --> 31:19.798
-HEAR, HEAR!
-YEAH.

31:19.800 --> 31:23.465
IN YEARS PAST, NOW,
I MIGHT'VE GONE ON AT LENGTH

31:23.467 --> 31:25.532
WORRYING A BELOVED THEME,

31:25.534 --> 31:29.065
TURNING IT AND TURNING IT ON
THE LATHE OF MY OWN SWEET VOICE.

31:29.067 --> 31:33.332
BUT, LISTEN, THERE ARE OTHER
VOICES THAT NEED TO BE HEARD,

31:33.334 --> 31:36.398
THAT DESERVE TO BE HEARD.

31:36.400 --> 31:40.532
SO I'M GOING TO TURN IT OVER
TO MY VERY WONDERFUL

31:40.534 --> 31:43.398
AND WISE WIFE-TO-BE,

31:43.400 --> 31:44.532
PASTOR MAE GREENLEAF.

31:44.534 --> 31:46.365
Together: AMEN!

31:46.367 --> 31:47.965
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT SHE'S GONNA SAY?

31:47.967 --> 31:49.298
DOES ANYONE EVER?

31:49.300 --> 31:52.631
I WANTED TO SAY A FEW WORDS
ABOUT PARTNERSHIP.

31:52.633 --> 31:54.565
MM-HMM.

31:54.567 --> 31:56.298
GODLY PARTNERSHIP.

31:56.300 --> 31:57.531
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

31:57.533 --> 31:59.199
DON'T BE RUDE.

31:59.201 --> 32:01.598
TO CALL FERNANDO AMABLE.

32:01.600 --> 32:07.865
NOW, YOU KNOW WE PARTNER
WITH GOD ON SOME THINGS.

32:07.867 --> 32:09.865
NOT ALL, LORD KNOWS, NOT ALL.

32:09.867 --> 32:11.165
[ LAUGHTER ]

32:11.167 --> 32:12.965
BUT SOME THINGS.

32:12.967 --> 32:18.199
BUT IT IS NOT
A 50-50 ARRANGEMENT.

32:36.134 --> 32:38.199
[ LOCK CLICKING ]

32:39.400 --> 32:40.632
[ LOCK DISENGAGES ]

32:43.334 --> 32:44.932
[ SIGHS ]

32:44.934 --> 32:46.399
AH.

32:50.067 --> 32:55.398
SINCE GOD IS THE LORD
OF ALL THINGS,

32:55.400 --> 33:00.665
THEN SPACE HAS TO BE LEFT FOR
GOD IN ALL HUMAN PARTNERSHIPS.

33:00.667 --> 33:01.998
AMEN?
Together: AMEN.

33:02.000 --> 33:06.598
Mae: I DON'T CARE IF YOU'RE
CONSIDERING MARRIAGE, AS I AM,

33:06.600 --> 33:11.132
OR SOME BUSINESS ARRANGEMENT.

33:11.134 --> 33:15.932
WHEN YOU MAKE A DEAL
WITH A HUMAN BEING,

33:15.934 --> 33:18.732
IF YOU FORM A PLATFORM,

33:18.734 --> 33:22.665
YOU HAD BETTER LEAVE SPACE
AT THAT TABLE FOR GOD.

33:22.667 --> 33:24.131
-AMEN!
-AMEN!

33:24.133 --> 33:27.932
BECAUSE HOW MANY OF US KNOW
THERE'S NO SUCH THING AS 50-50?

33:27.934 --> 33:33.565
BECAUSE WHERE IS THERE
ANY ROOM FOR GOD IN THAT?

33:33.567 --> 33:37.665
HOW IS HE GONNA SQUEEZE
THROUGH THAT DEATH TRAP?

33:37.667 --> 33:40.665
NO, THIS MARRIAGE IS NOT
GONNA BE 50-50.

33:40.667 --> 33:45.932
IT IS GOING TO BE WHATEVER
MY GOD WANTS IT TO BE.

33:45.934 --> 33:48.798
AND THAT IS HOW
IT'S GOING TO WORK.

33:48.800 --> 33:49.998
OH, MAKE US SMALL.

33:50.000 --> 33:52.499
OH, LORD, AS SMALL
AS YOU WANT US TO BE.

33:52.501 --> 33:55.898
YES. MAKE US NOTHING.

33:55.900 --> 34:00.598
AND IF ANYONE OFFERS YOU

34:00.600 --> 34:04.031
50-50 ON ANYTHING,

34:04.033 --> 34:09.498
YOU JUST SAY NO BECAUSE
WE HAVE TO LEAVE ROOM FOR GOD.

34:09.500 --> 34:11.498
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

34:11.500 --> 34:12.665
James: AMEN.

34:12.667 --> 34:14.232
HALLELUJAH!

34:14.234 --> 34:15.632
WE HAVE TO DO IT.

34:15.634 --> 34:19.432
-AMEN.
-AMEN.

34:19.434 --> 34:20.865
THAT WAS WONDERFUL.

34:21.967 --> 34:23.299
WELL DONE.

34:26.933 --> 34:28.199
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

34:31.600 --> 34:32.699
ZORA?

34:38.000 --> 34:39.465
[ DOOR OPENS ]

34:41.800 --> 34:43.532
ZORA?

34:43.534 --> 34:46.432
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

34:52.334 --> 34:54.398
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

34:54.400 --> 34:55.565
YOU WANT
TO BRING THAT INSIDE?

34:55.567 --> 34:57.365
OH.

34:57.367 --> 35:00.298
MY BAD. UH...

35:00.300 --> 35:04.398
JUST DROPPING OFF
THE REST OF NIKKI'S THINGS.

35:04.400 --> 35:06.265
THOUGHT YOU'D STILL BE UP
AT THAT PARTY.

35:06.267 --> 35:08.398
IT'S OKAY. SHE'S NOT HERE.

35:08.400 --> 35:11.732
SO...

35:11.734 --> 35:14.798
YOU'RE DANTE SAUNDERS?

35:14.800 --> 35:17.632
I WAS.
I'M CURRENTLY BENCHED.

35:19.434 --> 35:21.331
YOU HAVE ANY MORE BOXES?

35:21.333 --> 35:23.199
NO, NO.

35:23.201 --> 35:27.732
UH, I SHOULD PROBABLY
HEAD OUT, THEN.

35:31.534 --> 35:33.732
SO, YOU TWO ARE REALLY DONE,
HUH?

35:33.734 --> 35:35.232
WHO? ME AND NIK?

35:35.234 --> 35:37.265
YEAH.

35:37.267 --> 35:39.432
YEAH, IT SEEMS LIKE IT.

35:39.434 --> 35:42.265
SO, WHO ARE YOU?

35:42.267 --> 35:44.932
WELL,
I WAS THE ONLY DAUGHTER

35:44.934 --> 35:47.198
OF THE PRODIGAL PREACHER
GRACE GREENLEAF.

35:47.200 --> 35:51.132
NOW I DON'T KNOW WHO I AM.

35:51.134 --> 35:54.198
MM.

35:54.200 --> 35:58.398
WELL, UH...

35:58.400 --> 36:01.198
LET'S START
WITH YOUR NAME.

36:01.200 --> 36:02.732
SOPHIA.

36:02.734 --> 36:05.865
NICE TO MEET YOU, SOPHIA.

36:05.867 --> 36:07.999
NICE TO MEET YOU, TOO.

36:14.934 --> 36:18.598
YOU WANT
TO GO FOR A RIDE?

36:18.600 --> 36:20.665
WHERE?
WHEREVER.

36:20.667 --> 36:23.998
COOL JUST TO DRIVE
SOMETIMES, YOU KNOW?

36:24.000 --> 36:26.665
♪♪

36:26.667 --> 36:29.732
YEAH. SURE. WHY NOT?

36:29.734 --> 36:31.865
COOL.

36:31.867 --> 36:39.132
♪♪

36:39.134 --> 36:46.598
♪♪

36:46.600 --> 36:54.065
♪♪

36:54.067 --> 36:56.598
WHAT A FRICKING MESS.

36:56.600 --> 36:58.465
IF I HAD BEEN LET IN ON
WHAT YOU AND BOB WERE UP TO,

36:58.467 --> 37:00.798
I COULD HAVE CLEARED
A PATH FOR THIS THING.

37:00.800 --> 37:04.465
HE JUST TOLD ME
THREE DAYS AGO.

37:04.467 --> 37:07.865
SORRY.

37:07.867 --> 37:11.598
KEN FILED PAPERS
TO DIVORCE ME.

37:11.600 --> 37:14.665
YOU'RE HAPPY
WITH THIS WOMAN.

37:14.667 --> 37:16.099
WORST PARTY EVER.

37:19.067 --> 37:22.565
WAIT.
ARE YOU OKAY TO DRIVE?

37:22.567 --> 37:25.132
WHAT DO YOU CARE?

37:25.134 --> 37:28.598
YES, I'M OKAY TO DRIVE.

37:28.600 --> 37:31.632
♪♪

37:31.634 --> 37:33.698
[ VEHICLE DOOR CLOSES ]

37:33.700 --> 37:41.932
♪♪

37:41.934 --> 37:43.365
GOOD NIGHT.

37:48.334 --> 37:50.865
BRAVO!

37:50.867 --> 37:52.798
SOMEHOW,
I DON'T FEEL APPLAUDED.

37:52.800 --> 37:55.865
FIRST, THAT LITTLE PERFORMANCE
FOR THE SISTERS OF TAMAR.

37:55.867 --> 37:59.165
PERFORMANCE? EXCUSE ME?

37:59.167 --> 38:02.398
I HEARD ALL ABOUT IT.
"MY FATHER DID THIS.

38:02.400 --> 38:05.598
MY FATHER DID THAT. AND HE'S
NOT HERE TO CONTRADICT YOU.

38:05.600 --> 38:07.498
SO WHO'S TO KNOW
WHAT'S TRUE?"

38:07.500 --> 38:09.965
AND NOW THIS?

38:09.967 --> 38:14.465
YOU ARE A REGULAR ONE-WOMAN
REPERTORY THEATER. BRAVO.

38:14.467 --> 38:17.399
ARE YOU HONESTLY SUGGESTING
THAT I FABRICATED A STORY

38:17.401 --> 38:19.798
ABOUT BEING SEXUALLY ABUSED
BY MY OWN FATHER?

38:19.800 --> 38:22.198
AND GLORIFYING
AN IMPENDING WEDDING

38:22.200 --> 38:25.798
THAT'S NO MORE THAN A PLOY
TO WIN BACK THIS CHURCH.

38:25.800 --> 38:27.665
BRAVO.

38:27.667 --> 38:34.198
♪♪

38:34.200 --> 38:37.065
WONDERFUL PARTY, THOUGH.

38:37.067 --> 38:41.398
THANK YOU SO MUCH
FOR MY INVITATION.

38:41.400 --> 38:42.998
GO WITH GOD.

38:43.000 --> 38:49.998
♪♪

38:50.000 --> 38:51.798
GOOD NIGHT, MAE.

38:51.800 --> 38:56.499
♪♪

38:56.501 --> 38:58.265
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

38:58.267 --> 39:02.332
♪♪

39:02.334 --> 39:04.598
OH, COME IN.
I JUST PUT NATHAN DOWN.

39:04.600 --> 39:05.832
MM.

39:08.067 --> 39:09.665
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

39:09.667 --> 39:13.399
-MAY I?
-OH. OF COURSE, DADDY.

39:16.467 --> 39:19.798
SO, HE'S GREAT, RIGHT?

39:19.800 --> 39:22.732
I MEAN, WHEN YOU PUT ASIDE
EVERYTHING ELSE.

39:22.734 --> 39:25.265
PERHAPS,

39:25.267 --> 39:30.132
BUT YOUR MOTHER AND I
CAN'T PUT EVERYTHING ASIDE.

39:30.134 --> 39:32.399
NOT AT THIS POINT IN TIME.

39:32.401 --> 39:34.999
SO, YOU WANT ME
TO BREAK UP WITH HIM?

39:35.001 --> 39:37.932
NO, NO, NO.

39:37.934 --> 39:40.932
BUT WE WOULD LIKE YOU
TO PUT THINGS ON HOLD

39:40.934 --> 39:44.532
UNTIL GRACE BECOMES
PERMANENT HEAD PASTOR.

39:44.534 --> 39:47.798
THAT WAS THE PLAN.

39:47.800 --> 39:50.332
GRACE?

39:50.334 --> 39:53.332
GRACE FIRST.

39:53.334 --> 39:55.532
THEN ME.

39:55.534 --> 40:01.065
BABY, IF THIS IS THE GREAT LOVE
THAT GOD HAS FOR YOU,

40:01.067 --> 40:02.265
IT'LL KEEP.

40:03.934 --> 40:05.599
YOU PRAY ON IT.

40:09.467 --> 40:12.798
I'M SURE YOU'LL SEE
THE WISDOM IN THE MORNING.

40:12.800 --> 40:16.098
♪♪

40:16.100 --> 40:20.265
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

40:20.267 --> 40:22.765
♪♪

40:22.767 --> 40:26.198
SO, I WAS RIGHT
ABOUT THE PARTY.

40:26.200 --> 40:29.865
JUDEE, YOU MAY UNDERSTAND
THIS BETTER THAN ANYONE --

40:29.867 --> 40:34.532
MY PARENTS DO NOT ASK
MY PERMISSION -- EVER.

40:34.534 --> 40:37.532
WE NEED THE DEACONS TO VOTE
FOR THIS PLAN.

40:37.534 --> 40:40.299
WE NEED THOSE SEATS ON THE BOARD
TO MAKE IT MAKE SENSE.

40:42.200 --> 40:44.399
I KNOW
THAT'S HOW YOU SEE IT.

40:44.401 --> 40:47.731
IF YOU NEED A REASON TO SEE IT
A LITTLE MORE MY WAY,

40:47.733 --> 40:51.932
I'LL GIVE YOU ONE,
BUT I BEG YOUR DISCRETION

40:51.934 --> 40:54.765
BECAUSE EVEN PHIL
DOESN'T KNOW THIS.

40:54.767 --> 40:58.499
THIS NEW CAMPUS
THAT WE'RE PROPOSING,

40:58.501 --> 41:02.765
THIS NATIONAL LANDMARK,

41:02.767 --> 41:04.565
IT'S GOING TO BE RUN
BY YOU.

41:06.867 --> 41:08.798
YOU.

41:08.800 --> 41:10.932
NOT INTERIM.

41:10.934 --> 41:12.665
PERMANENT.

41:12.667 --> 41:14.265
DADDY HAS SAID.

41:14.267 --> 41:17.532
BUT IT'S ONLY GOING
TO HAPPEN

41:17.534 --> 41:20.932
IF YOU GET US
THOSE SEATS ON THE BOARD.

41:20.934 --> 41:26.198
♪♪

41:26.200 --> 41:29.465
YOU ARE
FULL OF SURPRISES.

41:29.467 --> 41:34.398
♪♪

41:34.400 --> 41:36.865
USE IT.

41:36.867 --> 41:38.598
SEND BOB THE RECORDING.

41:38.600 --> 41:40.799
WRITE THE E-MAIL, WHATEVER.
JUST DO IT.

41:44.934 --> 41:47.132
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

41:51.867 --> 41:53.932
